VIDEOS | DOWNTOWN LOUISVILLE BRIDGE

Video | Stay cables installed on the new downtown bridge span | 1:55

The first stay cable was installed today on the downtown bridge. The stay cables will hold up the deck on the new span. Michael Clevenger, The C-J

article_metadata.description: Thousands of Kentucky and Indiana residents posted pics and tweets using the hashtag #WalkTheBridge as the public walked Louisville's new Abraham Lincoln Bridge Saturday morning.
